In considering the active powers&#xD;<lb/>
which produce the phaenomenon&#xD;<lb/>
of Nature, it is not necessary&#xD;<lb/>
to enter upon any abstract&#xD;<lb/>
disquisitions upon the essence&#xD;<lb/>
of matter, or upon the&#xD;<lb/>
manner in which our sensations&#xD;<lb/>
are affected by the parts&#xD;<lb/>
of the external universe.-&#xD;<lb/>
