powers which produce this&#xD;<lb/>
beautiful arrangement.-&#xD;<lb/>
The phaenomenon which&#xD;<lb/>
is most constantly before&#xD;<lb/>
our eyes is the Attraction&#xD;<lb/>
of Matter.&#xD;<lb/>
- A stone thrown into the&#xD;<lb/>
atmosphere rapidly descends&#xD;<lb/>
to the earth.&#xD;<lb/>
Water <unclear xmlns:conf="https://www.lancaster.ac.uk/library/ns/digital-library/config/1.0">as</unclear> soon as it is&#xD;<lb/>
